Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: America's Day of Terror, 9/11
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sx6n8
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 14 Sep 2001
Alistair Cooke reflects on how he and the rest of the American population reacted to the World Trade Center terrorist attack on September 11th 2001.